WEBVTT

00:11:59.167 --> 00:12:01.893
Not just for a month or for a quarter

00:12:01.917 --> 00:12:03.292
but for years.

00:12:05.208 --> 00:12:07.458
So where does this leave us?

00:12:09.583 --> 00:12:13.976
Women in the workforce today
are constantly told,

00:12:14.000 --> 00:12:16.643
"You can be anything you want now.

00:12:16.667 --> 00:12:18.125
It's up to you."

00:12:19.708 --> 00:12:21.393
Women of color,

00:12:21.417 --> 00:12:24.143
for whom the wage gap is even larger,

00:12:24.167 --> 00:12:25.417
have heard it.

00:12:26.417 --> 00:12:31.583
The two-thirds of minimum-wage workers
who are women have heard it.